WEBVTT

00:00:34.813 --> 00:00:35.980
Finally.

00:00:36.063 --> 00:00:39.730
I finally got my power back.

00:00:39.813 --> 00:00:41.896
Once my demonic liver has fully grown,

00:00:41.980 --> 00:00:46.646
I will be unstoppable!

00:00:47.438 --> 00:00:52.563
AGENT FROM ABOVE

00:00:53.271 --> 00:00:57.271
TURNING THE WHEEL

00:01:15.480 --> 00:01:16.313
Han Chieh.

00:01:17.021 --> 00:01:18.146
What's wrong?

00:01:20.813 --> 00:01:23.230
Wu Tien-chi said
he put a demonic liver inside me.

00:01:24.146 --> 00:01:25.813
It isn't inside you anymore.

00:01:27.230 --> 00:01:28.313
Then why aren't I…

00:01:29.521 --> 00:01:30.480
I gave you mine.

00:01:43.063 --> 00:01:44.896
I'm the Third Crown Prince's agent.

00:01:45.521 --> 00:01:46.563
I can't die.

00:01:48.230 --> 00:01:49.855
One of the perks of the job.

00:01:52.355 --> 00:01:54.896
The doctor said my cancer
has already spread.

00:01:54.980 --> 00:01:57.438
I only have a few months left to live.

00:01:57.938 --> 00:02:00.896
You shouldn't waste your energy on me.

00:02:02.021 --> 00:02:04.105
I should've died over ten years ago.

00:02:04.896 --> 00:02:06.646
Every extra day is a gift.

00:02:07.605 --> 00:02:08.980
I got more than I deserved.

00:02:15.188 --> 00:02:16.146
Han Chieh.

00:02:17.855 --> 00:02:19.855
Can you win this time?

00:02:27.938 --> 00:02:29.230
When I win,

00:02:30.313 --> 00:02:31.563
We'll go back to the tree.

00:02:46.771 --> 00:02:50.146
The Demon King has regained his power.
I'm going to find him.

00:02:50.230 --> 00:02:52.063
-Take care of Leafy.
-I'll help you.

00:02:52.146 --> 00:02:54.688
How? You don't stand a chance
against that thing.

00:02:54.771 --> 00:02:57.021
I could at least
get a few rounds off at him.

00:02:57.521 --> 00:03:00.730
Take care of the neighbors and Leafy.
I'm counting on you.

00:03:19.521 --> 00:03:20.771
DONGFENG MARKET

00:03:47.396 --> 00:03:49.855
You're really something else,
you little punk.

00:03:49.938 --> 00:03:51.521
Still standing

00:03:52.021 --> 00:03:54.063
even without a liver.

00:03:54.646 --> 00:03:56.230
Once you get the demonic liver,

00:03:56.313 --> 00:04:00.271
physical pain like this
will be a distant memory.

00:04:00.355 --> 00:04:03.438
When that happens,
I doubt I'll still be human.

00:04:03.521 --> 00:04:04.480
I'm warning you.

00:04:04.563 --> 00:04:08.480
If you don't let the others go,
I won't let you put that liver inside me.

00:04:12.688 --> 00:04:16.813
You never planned on letting me
do it, did you?

00:05:25.730 --> 00:05:27.813
Nine Dragons Divine Fire Barrier.

00:05:28.355 --> 00:05:31.271
Same old trick again?

00:05:31.896 --> 00:05:34.021
Spit it out!

00:05:35.438 --> 00:05:36.355
Fuck you.

00:06:22.688 --> 00:06:24.313
I know I don't have much choice.

00:06:24.896 --> 00:06:26.271
But I don't think I'd win.

00:06:27.021 --> 00:06:27.896
I want you all in on this.

00:06:28.480 --> 00:06:32.230
I didn't choose you
for being young and a good fighter.

00:06:32.813 --> 00:06:33.646
Why did you choose me?

00:06:34.188 --> 00:06:38.021
You can save those innocent people.
It's all up to you.

00:06:40.938 --> 00:06:43.021
When I win,
we'll make your wish come true.

00:06:52.563 --> 00:06:53.980
How many have you hidden?

00:07:12.271 --> 00:07:14.980
I swallowed one just now.
Got four in my stomach.

00:07:15.063 --> 00:07:17.480
See for yourself
how many dragons are inside me.

00:07:30.313 --> 00:07:33.355
I can't beat you,
but I can destroy the demonic liver.

00:08:28.271 --> 00:08:30.605
You really don't know what's good for you.

00:08:31.938 --> 00:08:36.146
You'd rather burn to death
than be my agent.

00:08:37.855 --> 00:08:39.896
I'll ask you one last time.

00:08:40.980 --> 00:08:41.813
Will you

00:08:41.896 --> 00:08:43.896
be my agent?

00:08:44.938 --> 00:08:49.771
Or would you rather have
everyone here die along with you?

00:08:52.396 --> 00:08:53.771
Fall back. Now.

00:08:56.563 --> 00:08:58.646
Fuck! I'm one of you!

00:08:58.730 --> 00:09:02.271
The golden spells aren't working anymore.
They're about to get in.

00:09:02.355 --> 00:09:03.271
It's okay.

00:09:03.355 --> 00:09:05.021
They're everywhere.

00:09:08.313 --> 00:09:09.605
Hang in there, everyone!

00:09:15.980 --> 00:09:17.021
Who are you?

00:09:19.813 --> 00:09:22.230
-I've never seen you before.
-Yeah, who are you?

00:09:22.313 --> 00:09:23.896
-It's Leafy.
-The red ghost!

00:09:35.396 --> 00:09:36.313
Leafy!

00:09:38.896 --> 00:09:41.063
Stop her! She's lifting the spell!

00:09:42.355 --> 00:09:44.480
Sis Lo! Get the golden ink!

00:09:49.646 --> 00:09:50.646
Move!

00:09:58.480 --> 00:09:59.813
Go find Han Chieh!

00:10:19.480 --> 00:10:20.355
Release him!

00:10:42.105 --> 00:10:46.896
Was it you, weakling,
who killed my hellspawn?

00:11:02.021 --> 00:11:03.480
You're in over your head.

00:12:28.438 --> 00:12:30.730
You decided to show up, little punk.

00:12:32.146 --> 00:12:36.355
I thought you hated
these lousy sacks of skin?

00:12:37.021 --> 00:12:39.396
What? Feeling desperate?

00:12:39.480 --> 00:12:40.605
Demon King.

00:12:41.605 --> 00:12:43.688
How many times have I told you?

00:12:44.188 --> 00:12:46.730
You eat like a filthy pig. It's gross.

00:12:46.813 --> 00:12:50.146
Can't kill you on an empty stomach!

00:12:53.605 --> 00:12:55.855
All these years, I've been imagining

00:12:55.938 --> 00:12:58.896
how I'm gonna chop off your arms,
break your legs,

00:12:58.980 --> 00:13:00.646
tear you to pieces

00:13:00.730 --> 00:13:02.813
and finally get my vengeance.

00:13:04.813 --> 00:13:05.646
Fine.

00:13:06.646 --> 00:13:09.438
So when are we going to screw
those heavenly rules

00:13:09.521 --> 00:13:11.688
and have a proper fight
using our true forms?

00:13:11.771 --> 00:13:12.896
Soon.

00:13:12.980 --> 00:13:15.980
When I've devoured
every soul in the Human Realm,

00:13:16.063 --> 00:13:19.313
I'll become more powerful than the gods

00:13:19.980 --> 00:13:23.230
and rule over heaven, earth and hell.

00:13:26.105 --> 00:13:27.271
Not in this lifetime.

00:15:15.355 --> 00:15:16.730
Damn it.

00:15:17.230 --> 00:15:20.396
Wu Tien-chi's body is too weak.

00:15:20.480 --> 00:15:22.813
Otherwise, I'd easily defeat you.

00:15:22.896 --> 00:15:25.646
You're complaining
about using a human body.

00:15:26.855 --> 00:15:28.480
Then why not use your true form?

00:15:30.563 --> 00:15:32.771
If I use my true form,

00:15:32.855 --> 00:15:35.146
your agent from above will die.

00:15:35.230 --> 00:15:36.855
Could you live with that?

00:15:37.355 --> 00:15:39.730
Demon King,
you're on the verge of defeat.

00:15:39.813 --> 00:15:42.313
So you want to provoke me
into using my true form

00:15:42.396 --> 00:15:45.230
and violating the heavenly rule?

00:15:46.730 --> 00:15:49.646
I've already committed countless sins.

00:15:49.730 --> 00:15:51.271
But you're different.

00:15:51.896 --> 00:15:54.771
Violate the heavenly rule
and you'll be in deep trouble.

00:15:55.355 --> 00:15:58.438
You're too rebellious.
The gods will make you pay.

00:16:00.105 --> 00:16:01.146
Hey.

00:16:01.771 --> 00:16:05.438
Who do you think
channeled my spirit down here?

00:16:15.980 --> 00:16:19.021
The gods think I'm rebellious?
That's just for show.

00:16:19.105 --> 00:16:21.480
In private, they actually adore me.

00:16:21.980 --> 00:16:25.021
You gods are all hypocrites.

00:16:25.105 --> 00:16:27.563
Trying to play good cop, bad cop with me.

00:16:28.355 --> 00:16:30.313
The righteous path is hard to walk.

00:16:30.396 --> 00:16:31.896
So the gods

00:16:31.980 --> 00:16:35.563
must be even more ruthless than demons.

00:16:51.605 --> 00:16:52.813
You little punk.

00:16:52.896 --> 00:16:55.396
Your agent from above
may be one in a million,

00:16:55.480 --> 00:16:57.271
but there are far more evil people

00:16:57.355 --> 00:17:00.771
than good in the Human Realm.

00:17:00.855 --> 00:17:02.521
Cut the crap.

00:17:05.438 --> 00:17:10.355
Sooner or later I will defeat you,
Third Crown Prince.

00:17:10.438 --> 00:17:13.980
You're a lousy fighter,
but a pretty good escape artist.

00:17:26.480 --> 00:17:28.313
Please, have mercy on me.

00:17:30.063 --> 00:17:30.896
Give me a chance.

00:17:31.646 --> 00:17:33.896
I… I will mend my ways.

00:17:34.688 --> 00:17:36.146
I will do your bidding.

00:17:36.605 --> 00:17:39.313
I… I'll help you…

00:17:42.105 --> 00:17:44.396
You've been
a real pain in my ass recently.

00:17:44.855 --> 00:17:48.188
You know all those privileges
the Demon King promised you in hell?

00:17:48.271 --> 00:17:50.021
I've taken care of them for you.

00:17:51.105 --> 00:17:52.230
They're all gone.

00:17:55.563 --> 00:17:58.688
You must know what you deserve.

00:17:59.188 --> 00:18:00.480
Do me a favor.

00:18:01.146 --> 00:18:01.980
Jump.

00:18:11.938 --> 00:18:13.480
I can't go to hell, wait.

00:18:13.563 --> 00:18:14.688
I can't go to hell.

00:18:14.771 --> 00:18:17.480
Third Crown Prince, I beg you.
Give me another chance.

00:18:17.563 --> 00:18:20.188
Give me another chance. I beg you.

00:18:20.271 --> 00:18:22.313
Please, I really can't go to hell now.

00:18:22.396 --> 00:18:25.146
The gods have already
given you so many chances.

00:18:25.730 --> 00:18:28.480
But you always choose the most evil path.

00:18:29.688 --> 00:18:32.980
You brought this on yourself.
I can't help you.

00:18:36.896 --> 00:18:38.938
Han Chieh is a sinner.

00:18:39.438 --> 00:18:42.313
But he spent over ten years
atoning for his sins.

00:18:42.855 --> 00:18:45.605
He's even willing
to sacrifice himself to save others.

00:18:46.355 --> 00:18:47.438
What about you?

00:19:14.271 --> 00:19:15.105
Bad boy.

00:19:18.646 --> 00:19:21.730
Humans should deal with their own affairs.

00:20:04.063 --> 00:20:05.521
This old man again?

00:20:05.605 --> 00:20:10.271
Unsanctioned revenge
gets you punishment down there too.

00:20:17.230 --> 00:20:19.230
COMMAND

00:20:21.271 --> 00:20:23.271
A Black Command Token?

00:20:23.355 --> 00:20:25.355
Sorry. It's all above board.

00:20:32.396 --> 00:20:35.188
The gods have already
given you so many chances.

00:20:35.271 --> 00:20:36.646
You brought this on yourself.

00:20:44.896 --> 00:20:45.938
You're Wu Meng-hsueh?

00:20:46.021 --> 00:20:46.855
PURE EVIL

00:20:46.938 --> 00:20:48.105
You are…

00:20:48.188 --> 00:20:49.563
I'm Ox Head.

00:20:50.146 --> 00:20:52.063
Ox Head? Then this must be…

00:20:52.146 --> 00:20:55.146
Quit with the fucking questions.
Can't you see this is hell?

00:20:56.146 --> 00:20:57.313
You'd better behave.

00:20:57.396 --> 00:21:00.396
With your record,
you'll be here for hundreds of years.

00:21:17.605 --> 00:21:18.438
Han Chieh.

00:21:20.938 --> 00:21:21.813
Han Chieh.

00:21:23.146 --> 00:21:24.188
Han Chieh!

00:21:32.688 --> 00:21:33.563
Am I dead?

00:21:37.771 --> 00:21:38.938
Kid.

00:21:39.813 --> 00:21:41.313
Let me show you something.

00:21:47.480 --> 00:21:48.646
Where are my parents?

00:21:56.605 --> 00:21:57.855
Were they reborn?

00:21:59.813 --> 00:22:02.855
They stepped on the Wheel of Life
and were reborn

00:22:02.938 --> 00:22:05.646
when you agreed to become my agent.

00:22:06.980 --> 00:22:08.021
What?

00:22:09.438 --> 00:22:12.105
What you saw down here was an illusion.

00:22:12.188 --> 00:22:13.313
I deceived you.

00:22:15.063 --> 00:22:17.063
So they didn't suffer in hell

00:22:18.105 --> 00:22:18.980
because of me?

00:22:21.688 --> 00:22:23.188
You're the one who suffered.

00:22:39.313 --> 00:22:42.938
Chieh, we're about to be reincarnated.

00:22:43.021 --> 00:22:46.396
We won't remember you
after we drink the Soup of Oblivion,

00:22:46.480 --> 00:22:49.855
so this is our only chance to say goodbye.

00:22:49.938 --> 00:22:53.438
We worry about you
and we're going to miss you.

00:22:54.480 --> 00:22:57.855
We don't want you blaming yourself
and suffering needlessly.

00:22:59.230 --> 00:23:03.105
Chieh, let bygones be bygones.

00:23:03.605 --> 00:23:05.605
I want you to know

00:23:05.688 --> 00:23:08.813
that even if I don't remember you
in the next life,

00:23:08.896 --> 00:23:11.521
you'll always be our beloved son.

00:23:11.938 --> 00:23:13.021
Always.

00:23:13.771 --> 00:23:15.188
Remember that.

00:23:42.313 --> 00:23:45.105
Your parents
may not have raised you properly,

00:23:45.605 --> 00:23:48.355
but they didn't deserve
punishment in hell.

00:23:50.771 --> 00:23:52.021
So right from the start,

00:23:52.521 --> 00:23:53.980
I helped them be reborn.

00:23:55.271 --> 00:23:56.605
But as you know,

00:23:56.688 --> 00:24:00.313
that required pulling some strings.

00:24:01.938 --> 00:24:03.105
There's a price to pay.

00:24:03.605 --> 00:24:05.313
Your hard work these past years

00:24:05.396 --> 00:24:08.355
served as repayment for your initial debt.

00:24:09.313 --> 00:24:10.146
Congratulations.

00:24:11.021 --> 00:24:12.105
Initial debt?

00:24:13.021 --> 00:24:14.480
How much more do I owe you?

00:24:18.480 --> 00:24:20.063
Life and death are predestined.

00:24:20.646 --> 00:24:22.313
This girl is terminally ill.

00:24:23.063 --> 00:24:26.563
Not even I can prolong her life.

00:24:29.521 --> 00:24:30.480
I can't save her.

00:24:31.771 --> 00:24:32.980
But you saved me.

00:24:34.063 --> 00:24:37.396
You were determined to die back then.
I just made the most of it.

00:24:38.021 --> 00:24:41.021
Not everyone can become an agent
to pay off their debts.

00:24:46.813 --> 00:24:47.730
However…

00:24:50.105 --> 00:24:52.063
I can give her a new liver.

00:24:54.188 --> 00:24:57.438
Because her suffering
is the Demon King's doing.

00:25:15.021 --> 00:25:18.563
This golden liver can relieve the pain
caused by her illness,

00:25:18.646 --> 00:25:20.605
but it can't cure her or extend her life.

00:25:21.188 --> 00:25:23.896
How long she has left is down to fate.

00:25:25.188 --> 00:25:27.646
So she might not survive
even with this new liver?

00:25:29.730 --> 00:25:32.188
There's a price to pay for this too.

00:25:32.980 --> 00:25:34.313
MILK CAPS

00:25:35.313 --> 00:25:37.646
THIRD CROWN PRINCE'S AGENT
IN THE HUMAN REALM

00:25:38.396 --> 00:25:39.230
What's that?

00:25:40.396 --> 00:25:41.230
Contract renewal.

00:25:42.063 --> 00:25:45.230
As I said,
you owe me more than that initial debt.

00:25:45.313 --> 00:25:47.771
I, HAN CHIEH, AM WILLING
TO RENEW THE CONTRACT

00:25:47.855 --> 00:25:50.855
AND BE THE THIRD CROWN PRINCE'S AGENT
IN THE HUMAN REALM

00:25:52.771 --> 00:25:54.938
This golden liver is included in the deal.

00:25:55.021 --> 00:25:56.771
Final offer. Take it or leave it.

00:26:08.063 --> 00:26:09.188
I'll sign.

00:26:12.146 --> 00:26:13.355
HAN CHIEH

00:26:16.730 --> 00:26:18.980
THIRD CROWN PRINCE'S AGENT
IN THE HUMAN REALM

00:26:43.188 --> 00:26:44.021
Remember.

00:26:44.521 --> 00:26:46.396
Fumigate it with incense every day.

00:26:46.480 --> 00:26:47.771
After 49 days,

00:26:48.480 --> 00:26:50.230
Javvy will hatch.

00:26:54.355 --> 00:26:56.230
Before that happens,

00:26:56.813 --> 00:26:59.521
consider yourself on an extended vacation.

00:27:00.646 --> 00:27:02.855
Damn, am I nice or what?

00:27:03.855 --> 00:27:04.855
Third Crown Prince.

00:27:08.396 --> 00:27:09.855
There's one thing I don't get.

00:27:11.730 --> 00:27:12.813
Why me?

00:27:18.771 --> 00:27:20.313
You had so many better options.

00:27:22.355 --> 00:27:23.896
Why give me a second chance?

00:27:28.146 --> 00:27:30.355
FENGYUAN TEMPLE,
MARSHAL OF THE CENTRAL ALTAR

00:27:30.438 --> 00:27:31.688
You might not know it,

00:27:32.605 --> 00:27:34.730
but I've always been by your side.

00:27:37.521 --> 00:27:39.813
When you were little,
you loved riding bikes.

00:27:40.313 --> 00:27:42.896
You'd cycle around in front of me all day.

00:27:45.980 --> 00:27:48.313
-Chieh, why won't you listen?
-Stop running.

00:27:48.396 --> 00:27:52.688
The first time you defied your parents
was when you tried to keep a stray cat.

00:27:52.771 --> 00:27:53.855
-Listen!
-I want to keep it!

00:27:53.938 --> 00:27:56.063
Don't yell at him like that.

00:27:56.813 --> 00:27:58.313
You got your way that time.

00:27:59.355 --> 00:28:00.230
Hey!

00:28:00.313 --> 00:28:01.146
Let's go.

00:28:01.230 --> 00:28:05.896
Your first fight
was defending a classmate from bullies.

00:28:05.980 --> 00:28:07.688
FENGYUAN TEMPLE

00:28:17.521 --> 00:28:19.855
And on that day that haunts you,

00:28:21.105 --> 00:28:22.230
I was there too.

00:28:28.688 --> 00:28:30.146
I watched you grow up.

00:28:30.730 --> 00:28:32.521
I know the real you.

00:28:33.813 --> 00:28:36.188
Even though
you went astray and made mistakes,

00:28:36.730 --> 00:28:38.563
you never shirked responsibility.

00:28:40.021 --> 00:28:43.480
Who could possibly deserve
a second chance more than you?

00:28:46.105 --> 00:28:48.563
Do your best. I'm watching.

00:29:05.688 --> 00:29:08.146
QIANKUN HOOP

00:29:09.605 --> 00:29:11.146
FIRE-TIPPED SPEAR

00:29:12.230 --> 00:29:14.146
GOLDEN BRICK

00:29:14.730 --> 00:29:17.146
RED ARMILLARY SASH

00:29:17.230 --> 00:29:20.146
LEOPARD-SKIN POUCH

00:29:21.313 --> 00:29:23.105
WIND FIRE WHEELS

00:29:24.313 --> 00:29:26.813
NINE DRAGONS DIVINE FIRE BARRIER

00:29:56.521 --> 00:30:00.730
DONGFENG MARKET

00:30:11.021 --> 00:30:13.105
Han Chieh, here's the lighter you wanted.

00:30:46.813 --> 00:30:47.855
Any regrets?

00:30:48.980 --> 00:30:49.813
For what?

00:30:49.896 --> 00:30:51.646
Renewing your contract.

00:30:52.771 --> 00:30:54.521
In the end, Leafy…

00:31:01.896 --> 00:31:02.980
No regrets.

00:31:04.605 --> 00:31:05.855
It was a good deal.

00:31:07.105 --> 00:31:08.771
At least she was happy

00:31:10.021 --> 00:31:11.563
for those last few months.

00:31:39.355 --> 00:31:42.230
FROM: LEAFY
TO: HAN CHIEH

00:31:45.146 --> 00:31:47.605
How are you doing, Han Chieh?

00:31:48.771 --> 00:31:52.271
I'll already be gone
by the time you read this.

00:31:53.313 --> 00:31:57.521
This is the last time I'll write so much,
so bear with me here

00:31:57.605 --> 00:31:59.271
and read until the end.

00:32:02.355 --> 00:32:05.230
After I got sick, I often thought

00:32:05.813 --> 00:32:08.771
that I should do something
to give my life meaning.

00:32:10.188 --> 00:32:14.021
Confused and lost, I went to
Dongfeng Market for the first time.

00:32:14.855 --> 00:32:17.271
I met you and everyone else.

00:32:18.230 --> 00:32:21.980
There, I realized that death
is just another form of existence,

00:32:22.063 --> 00:32:23.313
so I stopped being afraid.

00:32:23.396 --> 00:32:25.771
A new friend? Won't you introduce us?

00:32:26.771 --> 00:32:30.355
I felt so much love in my final moments.

00:32:31.480 --> 00:32:34.146
It was the happiest time of my life.

00:32:34.230 --> 00:32:35.480
GET WELL SOON!

00:32:35.563 --> 00:32:37.146
LEAFY, GET WELL SOON!

00:32:37.230 --> 00:32:38.480
LET'S GO ABROAD AGAIN!

00:32:38.563 --> 00:32:42.563
Han Chieh, I didn't have time
to do all the things I wanted.

00:32:43.063 --> 00:32:45.896
I want someone to do them for me.

00:32:46.563 --> 00:32:49.855
Please play some video games
with the old guard for me.

00:32:50.896 --> 00:32:52.980
Please be kinder to yourself.

00:32:54.146 --> 00:32:57.855
And lastly, I have one small favor to ask.

00:32:58.896 --> 00:33:02.563
Please love this world for me
with all your heart.

00:33:03.063 --> 00:33:05.230
Even if it can be chaotic

00:33:05.313 --> 00:33:07.771
and the gods
don't seem to do anything about it.

00:33:08.855 --> 00:33:12.688
I believe what really changes the world

00:33:13.188 --> 00:33:16.271
is the hopes and dreams
of ordinary people like us.

00:33:26.563 --> 00:33:28.063
I did good, right?

00:33:28.771 --> 00:33:34.896
IN LOVING MEMORY OF MY LATE FATHER
CHANG HO-CHENG

00:33:34.980 --> 00:33:37.355
-Self-draw.
-A White Dragon? Wow.

00:33:37.438 --> 00:33:38.730
Come and have some food.

00:33:38.813 --> 00:33:42.646
-Good thing I didn't discard mine earlier.
-You should've done. Why keep it?

00:33:42.730 --> 00:33:44.355
You're pretty good at this.

00:33:46.730 --> 00:33:50.021
Third Crown Prince,
please watch over my son.

00:33:50.105 --> 00:33:52.771
Bless him with success at work

00:33:52.855 --> 00:33:55.605
and with good health.

00:33:56.396 --> 00:33:57.355
Hear my prayer.

00:34:04.563 --> 00:34:05.563
Han Chieh.

00:34:06.271 --> 00:34:09.896
Would you believe it
if I said there really was world peace?

00:34:21.438 --> 00:34:24.438
WORLD PEACE

00:34:28.605 --> 00:34:29.896
Make a wish.

00:34:36.021 --> 00:34:38.188
MARSHAL OF THE CENTRAL ALTAR

00:34:39.396 --> 00:34:43.105
I believe
that magic can't overcome divine power,

00:34:43.188 --> 00:34:45.230
divine power can't overcome karma

00:34:45.313 --> 00:34:47.063
and karma can't overcome willpower.

00:34:49.771 --> 00:34:55.146
So the most powerful person in the world
is someone with a wish.

00:35:02.938 --> 00:35:09.896
WORLD PEACE, MARSHAL OF THE CENTRAL ALTAR

00:35:20.230 --> 00:35:23.771
DONGFENG MARKET

00:35:59.563 --> 00:36:00.688
Who are you?

00:36:00.771 --> 00:36:02.146
Hello there.

00:36:09.063 --> 00:36:10.063
You brought a ghost?

00:36:10.146 --> 00:36:14.771
No way, you can actually see him?
I'm impressed, Master Han.

00:36:15.355 --> 00:36:16.230
I'm Mr. Li.

00:36:16.313 --> 00:36:17.480
-I have some--
-Hold up.

00:36:18.646 --> 00:36:20.438
-Mr. Li, right?
-Yes.

00:36:22.438 --> 00:36:23.980
MR. LI HIRED A GHOST

00:36:24.063 --> 00:36:27.480
TO KILL HIS ELDERS
AND INHERIT THEIR MONEY

00:36:27.563 --> 00:36:28.980
KICK HIS ASS

00:36:32.438 --> 00:36:33.646
Wait!

00:36:33.730 --> 00:36:35.646
I came to discuss business with you.

00:36:35.730 --> 00:36:37.771
Shouldn't you ask your boss first?

00:36:42.855 --> 00:36:46.563
I don't need to ask him.
His instructions have never changed.

00:36:47.021 --> 00:36:47.855
QIANKUN HOOP

00:36:58.313 --> 00:36:59.188
Eliminate evil.

00:37:07.021 --> 00:37:10.605
AGENT FROM ABOVE

00:37:25.688 --> 00:37:28.230
Money makes the world go round.

00:37:29.063 --> 00:37:31.938
Hell is even more corrupt
than the Human Realm.

00:37:32.646 --> 00:37:36.271
All your debts can be paid off.

00:37:39.521 --> 00:37:41.813
With this Hell Talisman…

00:37:44.438 --> 00:37:46.105
you can alter karma

00:37:47.313 --> 00:37:49.438
any way you please.

00:37:49.521 --> 00:37:51.771
HELL TALISMAN

00:38:08.646 --> 00:38:10.021
Come!

00:38:39.980 --> 00:38:41.521
There is somebody

00:38:42.480 --> 00:38:43.813
I want you to kill.